### Test Category Trends Endpoint - 30 days
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/category-trends?period=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test Category Trends Endpoint - 90 days
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/category-trends?period=90
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test Category Trends Endpoint - 365 days
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/category-trends?period=365
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test Category Trends Endpoint - Invalid period (should fail)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/category-trends?period=7d
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test Category Trends Endpoint - No period (should default to 30)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/gov/analytics/category-trends
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
